PrecisAmendments to the MILITARY RULES OF EVIDENCE which revise subsections 31(2), (3) and (4), paragraph 79(1) and sections 85 and 86 in order to ensure that rules of evidence at trials by court martial are consistent with those applicable to trials before a civil court in a criminal case.
